# Vercel Deployment Environment Variables

## For Client (Frontend)
VITE_API_URL=https://your-server-url.vercel.app/api

## For Server (Backend)
CLIENT_ORIGIN=https://your-client-url.vercel.app
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-here-generate-with-openssl-rand-base64-32
DB_PATH=./src/data/evalops.db
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini